{"title":"CSS 自动生成 .d.ts","uid":"40c248981d4dc9431fe8a0d461ef29a9","slug":"2021-06-10scss2type","date":"2021-06-10T13:30:47.000Z","updated":"2023-02-20T21:20:56.455Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/2021-06-10scss2type.json","keywords":null,"cover":"https://img.zcool.cn/community/011b955568ef2700000127166e3178.jpg@1280w_1l_2o_100sh.jpg","content":"<h2 id=\"CSS-Module-Typed\"><a href=\"#CSS-Module-Typed\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"CSS Module Typed\"></a>CSS Module Typed</h2><p><strong>vscode 插件列表中有好多个，不要安装错了</strong></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://t-blog-images.aijs.top/img/20220607152316.webp\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"address\"><a href=\"#address\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"address\"></a>address</h2><p><a href=\"https://marketplace.visualstudio.com/items?itemName=awwit.typed-css-modules-plugin\">link</a></p>\n<h2 id=\"Install\"><a href=\"#Install\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Install\"></a>Install</h2><p>Install deps first:</p>\n<h3 id=\"require\"><a href=\"#require\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"require\"></a>require</h3><p><code>npm install typed-css-modules</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"if-you-need-less\"><a href=\"#if-you-need-less\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if you need less\"></a>if you need less</h3><p><code>npm install less</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"if-you-need-scss-x2F-sass\"><a href=\"#if-you-need-scss-x2F-sass\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if you need scss&#x2F;sass\"></a>if you need scss&#x2F;sass</h3><p><code>npm install sass</code></p>\n<h3 id=\"if-you-need-stylus\"><a href=\"#if-you-need-stylus\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"if you need stylus\"></a>if you need stylus</h3><p><code>npm install stylus</code></p>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>Modules can be installed globally. yarn is supported.</p></blockquote>\n<blockquote><span class=\"custom-blockquote-svg\"><svg width=\"24\" height=\"24\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\" data-reactroot=\"\">\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M22 12C22 6.5 17.5 2 12 2C6.5 2 2 6.5 2 12C2 17.5 6.5 22 12 22C13.8 22 15.5 21.5 17 20.6L22 22L20.7 17C21.5 15.5 22 13.8 22 12Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path fill=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\" undefined=\"1\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M17 8.5C15.23 8.97 14.07 10.84 14.01 13.27C14 13.33 14 13.4 14 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M9 8.5C7.23 8.97 6.07 10.84 6.01 13.27C6 13.33 6 13.4 6 13.47V13.5\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M15.97 11.5H16.04C17.12 11.5 18 12.38 18 13.47V13.53C18 14.62 17.12 15.5 16.03 15.5H15.96C14.88 15.5 14 14.62 14 13.53V13.46C14 12.38 14.88 11.5 15.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n<path stroke-linejoin=\"round\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-miterlimit=\"10\" stroke-width=\"2\" stroke=\"\" d=\"M7.97 11.5H8.04C9.12 11.5 10 12.38 10 13.47V13.53C10 14.62 9.12 15.5 8.03 15.5H7.97C6.88 15.5 6 14.62 6 13.53V13.46C6 12.38 6.88 11.5 7.97 11.5Z\"></path>\n</svg>\n</span><p>To switch the package manager (npm or yarn), you need to change the settings npm.packageManager of the built-in module vscode.npm.</p></blockquote>\n<h3 id=\"Configuring\"><a href=\"#Configuring\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"Configuring\"></a>Configuring</h3><p>By default, the option to automatically format .d.ts files using eslint is enabled. You can disable this feature through the setting “typed-css-modules.eslint.enable”: false.</p>\n<p>Usage<br>put</p>\n<p><code>// @type</code></p>\n<p>or</p>\n<p><code>/* @type */</code></p>\n<p>ahead of your .css&#x2F;.less&#x2F;.scss&#x2F;.sass&#x2F;.styl file, and save, you will get a d.ts file in same directory.</p>\n<h3 id=\"preview\"><a href=\"#preview\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"preview\"></a>preview</h3><p><img src=\"https://s2.ax1x.com/2019/01/31/k1yTT1.gif\"></p>\n<h3 id=\"demo\"><a href=